Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.mobile

Provides classes and interfaces defining the mobility service and the message contents used for requiring its execution.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mobile
    The Mobile class provide a partial implementation of an actor behavior that provides a method for creating mobile actors.
    Mobiler
    The Mobiler class support the moving of actors to another actor space.
    MobileReference
    The MobileReference class defines the references used by mobile actors.
    MobileState
    The MobileState class defines the state of a mobile actor that contains all the information for moving it in a new actor space.
    Mover
    The Mover class defines a behavior that moves the actor to another actor space.
